  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201311/f14f8c4d108a4be499b9d4d8fbf7cf3a.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t2014的考研考试越来越近了，下面为大家整理了考研英语作文万能模版，以供大家练习学习，希望能够帮助大家提高写作水平，在2014考研中取得更高的分数。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>Directions:</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>Write an essay of 160~200 words based on the following drawing. In your essay, you should</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>1) describe the drawing briefly,</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>2) explain its intended meaning, and then</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>3) support your view with an example/examples.</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>You should write neatly on ANSWER SHEET 2. (20 points)</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t范文：</p>\n<p>\n\tIn the picture, there shapes a sharp conflict between the goal keeper and the ball player. The former exaggerates the goal and minimizes himself in his mind while the latter thinks otherwise. Actually, both the goal and the keeper are just in normal size. What causes the problem is that they have overestimated the difficulty they are each faced with. Such attitude towards difficulty will surely produce negative effects on the results.</p>\n<p>\n\tDifficulties are in the pathway of everyone. To overcome them, we must at first make correct judgment on the situation, which is based on confidence, courage and rational thinking. Lets take memory for example. In the process of learning, students need to remember a lot of things, such as Chemical Elements Periodic Table, ancient articles and mathematical formulae. But many complain that it is hard to remember them accurately and they are ready to give up when they feel so. On the contrary, those who learn successfully are confident about themselves and willing to try although they also feel difficult at first. And later they find the more they practise the memory, the easier it becomes to remember.</p>\n<p>\n\tIn conclusion, if we are to succeed in handling the difficult things, we must have self confidence, judge the situation rationally and be courageous enough to keep trying.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>更多考研英语作文模板点击&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong><a href=\"http://kaoyan.hjenglish.com/zt/kyyyzw/\" target=\"_blank\">http://kaoyan.hjenglish.com/zt/kyyyzw/</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p546597/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p546597\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p547932/\">10大危险信号：你需要好好休息下了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p547944/\">美国小狗外形酷似希特勒爆红网络</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p547560/\">看世界：一生必去的27个地方（下）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548143/\">突击传统文化词汇，迎接四六级段落翻译</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548117/\">贝克汉姆买4亿豪宅 和威廉王子做邻居</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548160/\">骆驼也卖萌！不请自来与主人共进早餐</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p547254/\">大学里你学不到的7个人生技能</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548172/\">奥巴马2013年感恩节致辞（视频）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548358/\">想吃就吃才能瘦！吃巧克力也能减肥</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http